	SPACE	4,10
**	CAB	-  CHECK ABORT
*
*	CAB WAITS FOR A REVOLUTION OF THE DISK WHILE MONITORING THE
*	ABORT FLAG.  AFTER ONE COMPLETE RPM, ANY ATTEMPTS TO ABORT
*	ARE FUTILE.
*
*
*	ENTRY	NONE
*	EXIT	(PSW)	=  'Z' CLEAR IF     TO ABORT
*			=  'Z' SET   IF NOT TO ABORT
*	USES	A,F,D
*

CAB	CALL	READY

	ERRNZ	*-CAB.							/3.0a/
*	CALL	CAB.							/3.0a/
*	RET								/3.0a/

CAB.	LDA	S.CAADR+1
	ANA	A		Non-Zero => abort
	RET
